{"tid":2099374,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"過去5年有兩名警員被法庭質疑證供可信度受紀律處分","createTime":"2020-07-08T07:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T08:03:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f96f14a36b3f64a013a66f7b6319ab546117f3","tid":2099374,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:43:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536542-20200708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536542-20200708.htm&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDKxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=15a1e4fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536542-20200708.htm&h=33d77330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536542-20200708.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，過去5年有兩名警員因被法庭質疑證供可信度，受紀律處分，包括發出輕微違紀行為報告以及受譴責，沒有警員因干犯 《刑事罪行條例》的「宣誓下作假證供」而被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨議員譚文豪提出書面質詢，指有裁判官近日形容作供警員並非誠實可靠。保安局回覆表示，法庭可基於不同理由不接受控方證人的證供，例如未能在毫無合理疑點下信納證人證供，不一定代表證人不誠實可靠或解作虛假陳述。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">保安局又指出，政府並無計劃設立資料庫，紀錄法庭認定為並非誠實可靠的警員。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"cbdce8db5f648705024e43c02b316665503ce42b","tid":2099374,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"另一邊廂不停迫害正當法官 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d1b27156281b7886c03f4d91e57547bef944de","tid":2099374,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbdce8db5f648705024e43c02b316665503ce42b","tid":2099374,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"另一邊廂不停迫害正當法官 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets